title: Stimulus, Vaccine Plan, Rep. Andy Levin
itunes:title: Stimulus, Vaccine Plan, Rep. Andy Levin
description:
Host: Jeanne Sheehan Zaino, Iona College Professor. Guests: Rick Davis, Bloomberg contributor and former campaign manager for John McCain's 2008 presidential campaign, Joe Crowley, former New York Congressman and Democratic Caucus Chair, and Rep. Andy Levin, a Democrat representing Michigan's 9th Congressional District.
